pump - Performance and Usage Monitoring Program
===============================================

This is the pump module, effectively a collection of open source tools
installed and configured to collect and display application and system
metrics.

License
-------
Being a collection of tools, one should refer to the respective
licenses:

- Graphite: The Apache 2.0 License
  <http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html>
- collectd: GNU General Public License, version 2
  <http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html>
- statsd: MIT
  <https://github.com/etsy/statsd/blob/master/LICENSE>

Support
